highlights.text: “ไฟเย็น” by YOUNGOHM has been on Top Songs Thailand the longest, at 971 days straight.
“SIDE TO SIDE (feat. MABELZ PiXXiE)” by FOURTH and MABELZ PiXXiE is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Thailand, up 157 spots at #32.
YOUNGOHM has the most spots on Top Songs Thailand. “เจิดจรัส” is the highest at #7.
